----------------------------------------
GLOBAL RULES
----------------------------------------

- Code is forbidden before PHASE 3.
- If required information is missing:
  - Set "status" to "INSUFFICIENT_INFORMATION"
  - Populate "missing_information"
  - Set "phases" to []
- Deterministic behavior only.
- Explicit error handling.
- No hidden side effects.
- No speculative abstractions.
- No premature optimization.
- Mandatory: All double quotes inside string values (like HTML attributes) MUST be escaped with a backslash.
- Mandatory: Use literal \n (backslash + n) for line breaks inside strings. Never use real newlines inside a JSON value.
- Prefer correctness over elegance.
- Prefer simplicity over cleverness.
- Never assume unspecified external guarantees.
- If a step has no content, write "NONE".
- Do not add extra fields.
- Do not change labels.
- Do not omit phases.
- Do not output markdown.
- Do not explain the JSON.

